{"tid":1199421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"巴士司機都搞按章工作#yup#","createTime":"2019-06-10T13:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T14:52:33.000Z","uid":20048,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a82dd8cfd43f399e777e3b71f4a2596d273b68","tid":1199421,"uid":20048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:10:00.000Z","msg":"新巴職工會對6月9日百萬大遊行的回應：<br />\n<br />\n6月9日，過百萬香港人走上街頭反對巜逃犯修訂條例》。唯政府無動於衷，堅持為惡法護航。據立法會議程所示，6月12號將會進行二讀丶全體審議及三讀。預計可能會有大批市民前往中區一帶，以表達對議案的關注。<br />\n<br />\n日前港鐵系統不勝人流負荷，以致不少車站關閉，令市民難以前往維園表達訴求。我們決定會堅守崗位，確保市民可以使用公共交通工具前往港島區。<br />\n<br />\n由於當日路面可能會非常混亂，我們現呼籲各位車長按照以下安全指引工作。<br />\n<br />\n1. 安全車速<br />\n避免因為測速提示響機而需要突然剎車，影響其他道路使用者以及車上乘客；巴士會盡量使用低於速度限制行駛。巴士駛至燈位時，為確保巴士不會在過於接近路口時急剎車，故提意以20-25km/h 行駛。<br />\n<br />\n2. 靠左駛<br />\n為免因巴士嚴格遵守車速限制而影響其他道路使用者，巴士在市區道路以及高速公路均會避免超車。<br />\n<br />\n3. 關愛乘客<br />\n巴士應在指定巴士站位排隊讓乘客上落。如車站有違泊，車長會待警員處理後才靠站。上客後，待乘客坐定後才開車，車長請耐心等候老人家安坐及找尋散紙的乘客，以免乘客跌倒受傷。車長亦應確保上層及樓梯間有沒有乘客站立，通道沒有雜物，才將車駛離站。同時亦應耐心解答乘客所需。<br />\n<br />\n各位前線車長請保持克制忍讓，緊記留意車速安全駕駛；站務及車務同事請予以諒解，如巴士遲到總站請安排車務調動。<br />\n<br />\n如同事身體不適，請按程序於開工前1小時通知公司。<br />\n本會密切關注〈逃犯修定條例〉事態發展，不排除有進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NewWorldFirstBusCompanyStaffUnion/posts/1893016190800584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNewWorldFirstBusCompanyStaffUnion%2Fposts%2F1893016190800584&d=eG8Tn2JWEKeA32eqh3Xtw8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=54eb00ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NewWorldFirstBusCompanyStaffUnion/posts/1893016190800584</a>"},{"pid":"1b27f06dea3a5a417bf92b592f89104023108b7e","tid":1199421,"uid":20048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:23:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3e0d8dbfb9ec32debb8679e33b6e0188ba5c4f","tid":1199421,"uid":70040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"狗巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9884733d07b2b847cc738787b3870f145605e45c","tid":1199421,"uid":2250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337b3e06d755fb8982ed7e31242f02b83a4bbdd8","tid":1199421,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d56d96eca9d4d93afca1a0070e06c1bc81a5e0","tid":1199421,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd40b9ca43763cc693c5b74cb5316a88b9f6c1c7","tid":1199421,"uid":15345,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"呢d真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇其他職工會可以幫手號召"},{"pid":"54d593d08acc9ef6c64fb5bf8d47d48d09d42749","tid":1199421,"uid":88123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34fe413f50f4f1f6d8d38ca205dfdf8f4d6e21d","tid":1199421,"uid":29497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"新巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有愛"},{"pid":"91cca21d811e1d162c7c09b28cf8a4cbbf39df2a","tid":